1, install cmake for linux
sudo apt-get install cmake-curses-gui

warning: 'ldconfig' not found in PATH or not executable
Just prefix the sudo call with the redefinition of the PATH variable:
PATH=/usr/local/sbin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/sbin:/usr/bin:/sbin:/bin 

2, install pyqt via conda
install conda with python 3.6
conda uninstall pyqt
conda install pyqt=4

3, build vtk 7.1.1
install path: /home/guotai/install
set the following environment variables

export PATH="/home/guotai/install/bin:$PATH"
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH="/home/guotai/install/lib:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH"
export PYTHONPATH="/home/guotai/install/lib/python2.7/site-packages/vtk/:$PYTHONPATH"


4, build qt (optional)
install place:  /usr/local/Trolltech/Qt-4.8.7/

5, instal nibabel, scikit-image
